OL,3,CUK introduces visa bans on four
OL,4,Ccountries to stop 'abuse'
OL,6,FThe UK has put emergency visa bans on
OL,7,Ffour countries after accusing migrants
OL,8,Fof exploiting Britain's asylum system.
OL,10,FStudy visas for nationals from
OL,11,FAfghanistan, Cameroon, Myanmar, and
OL,12,FSudan have been halted, as have work
OL,13,Fvisas for Afghans.
OL,15,FThe government has placed an emergency
OL,16,Fbrake on the visa routes as it claims
OL,17,Fa growing number of people from these
OL,18,Fcountries are using legal migration
OL,19,Froutes as a backdoor to claim asylum
OL,20,Fin the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
