OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772662285
OL,3,CUK introduces visa bans on four
OL,4,Ccountries to stop 'abuse'
OL,6,FIt's the first time such visa bans
OL,7,Fhave been used by the UK government,
OL,8,Fin a step the Home Office has
OL,9,Fdescribed as "unprecedented".
OL,11,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood said:
OL,12,F"Britain will always provide refuge to
OL,13,Fpeople fleeing war and persecution,
OL,14,Fbut our visa system must not be abused.
OL,16,F"That is why I am taking the
OL,17,Funprecedented decision to refuse visas
OL,18,Ffor those nationals seeking to exploit
OL,19,Four generosity.
