OL,3,CUK introduces visa bans on four
OL,4,Ccountries to stop 'abuse'
OL,6,F"I will restore order and control to
OL,7,Four borders."
OL,9,FAccording to Home Office figures, some
OL,10,F39% of the 100,000 who claimed asylum
OL,11,Fin 2025 did so after arriving in the
OL,12,FUK through a legal migration route,
OL,13,Flike a study visa.
OL,15,FAsylum applications by students from
OL,16,FAfghanistan, Cameroon, Myanmar, and
OL,17,FSudan represent the most significant
OL,18,Fpart of a spike between 2021 and
OL,19,FSeptember 2025, the Home Office added.
