OL,3,CUK introduces visa bans on four
OL,4,Ccountries to stop 'abuse'
OL,6,FThe visa ban will be officially
OL,7,Fintroduced via an immigration rules
OL,8,Fchange on Thursday, when Mahmood is
OL,9,Falso expected to lay out other
OL,10,Fmeasures to toughen the UK asylum
OL,11,Fsystem.
