OL,3,CUK introduces visa bans on four
OL,4,Ccountries to stop 'abuse'
OL,6,FUnder the widely trailed plans, asylum
OL,7,Fseekers in the UK will have their
OL,8,Frefugee status reviewed every 30
OL,9,Fmonths in an effort to make the UK
OL,10,Fless attractive for illegal immigrants.
OL,12,FRefugees whose countries are deemed
OL,13,Fsafe will be expected to return home.
OL,15,FThe Home Secretary has previously
OL,16,Fthreatened a similar halt to all UK
OL,17,Fvisas for Angola, Namibia, and the
OL,18,FDemocratic Republic of Congo in
OL,19,FNovember, unless their governments
OL,20,Fagreed to take back illegal migrants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
