OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772662285
OL,3,CUK introduces visa bans on four
OL,4,Ccountries to stop 'abuse'
OL,6,FThis led to co-operation agreements
OL,7,Fwith all three countries, and illegal
OL,8,Fmigrants being returned via
OL,9,Fdeportation flights.
OL,11,FLast week, the government announced
OL,12,Fthat it will only grant asylum seekers
OL,13,Fwith refugee status temporary
OL,14,Fprotection, meaning their cases will
OL,15,Fbe reviewed every 30 months rather
OL,16,Fthan every five years.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
